1
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,080
All our sorrows.

2
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:24,080
I have found the key evidence.

3
00:01:24,520 --> 00:01:27,320
It's hidden in the lotus pond of the mansion.

4
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,360
No need to look.

5
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:46,280
There is no evidence in the lotus pond.

6
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:49,039
I just said that to test you.

7
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,840
What evidence?

8
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,880
I was just passing by.

9
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:55,880
Yan'er.

10
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:58,600
Why?

11
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:03,840
Ever since you said you escaped from the bandits,

12
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:08,639
to all the big and small things that happened on this journey,

13
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:12,330
including how you tried to kill me yesterday,

14
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:14,400
I've always been hoping against hope,

15
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,860
unwilling to suspect you.

16
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,840
Until I saw you now.

17
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,920
Why did you do this?

18
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,480
Why?

19
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:26,960
You ask me why?

20
00:02:28,760 --> 00:02:29,720
Sister.

21
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,560
You look so innocent.

22
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,720
You care about me so much.

23
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:39,160
I am your own sister.

24
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:41,640
Don't I know you?

25
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:45,079
You have all been fooled by her.

26
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,079
Sister.

27
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,680
Don't you care about me?

28
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,640
Why didn't you tell them

29
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,800
how I ended up in Qihong Brothel?

30
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:57,100
You ended up in Qihong Brothel

31
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:59,320
because of the witchcraft case back then.

32
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:01,320
What does it have to do with Zhaoxue?

33
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:04,900
She was the one who was supposed to end up in Qihong Brothel.

34
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:07,160
If she hadn't played tricks,

35
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,840
I would be the one who stayed.

36
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:13,240
I would be the one favored by Lord Fang.

37
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:14,960
So.

38
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:18,079
So you did all this?

39
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,520
So you wanted to kill me?

40
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:22,840
That's right.

41
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,760
I just wanted to kill you.

42
00:03:28,079 --> 00:03:31,040
I will take away everything you want.

43
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,400
Don't you like Lord Fang?

44
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,760
I insist on marrying him.

45
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:40,960
Yan'er.

46
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,780
It was my fault in the past.

47
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,720
I will figure something out.

48
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:47,960
I apologize to you.

49
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,320
Please don't be like this, okay?

50
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,120
Yan'er.

51
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:52,900
Let me make it up to you.

52
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:53,960
Make it up?

53
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:58,880
How can you make it up when you took everything that belonged to me?

54
00:03:58,880 --> 00:03:59,960
Su Qingyan.

55
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,040
Zhaoxue has been trying so hard for years

56
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:07,360
to save you from Qihong Brothel.

57
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:10,720
She investigated the case with me

58
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:13,580
so that I could help you get rid of your slave status.

59
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:17,760
I wanted you to return to the capital and wait for news.

60
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:20,360
She was worried that you would be in danger alone in the capital,

61
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:22,320
so she begged me to take you with us.

62
00:04:23,280 --> 00:04:25,080
As for you wanting to marry me,

63
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:27,770
she wasn't mad that you wanted to marry me,

64
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,760
but worried that you would be wronged

65
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:30,880
and disrespected.

66
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,280
Do you understand?

67
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:33,409
I don't understand.

68
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:36,820
It's not like that.

69
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:39,380
She is not that kind of person.

70
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:40,760
I know her.

71
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:43,840
Yan'er.

72
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,320
Turn back.

73
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,960
Don't do this anymore.

74
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:51,800
Yan'er.

75
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:55,880
Let's go live a good life together, okay?

76
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:58,820
Don't make any more mistakes.

77
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:00,320
Sister.

78
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,720
I can't turn back.

79
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:07,320
Master Huang Wansan is imprisoned in the Imperial Prison.

80
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:09,520
If he exposes the itinerary to Jinzhou,

81
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,560
what should we do?

82
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:13,690
I'm just afraid he won't expose it.

83
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,160
Time is running out.

84
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:16,760
Go to Jinzhou immediately.

85
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:17,520
Yes.

86
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:23,680
If the Second Miss Su tells me

87
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:26,530
where exactly the letters from ten years ago are,

88
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:30,760
I can remove the brand on your forehead.

89
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,440
Really?

90
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:39,360
If the Second Miss Su is willing to tell me

91
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:42,400
where exactly the letters from ten years ago are,

92
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:46,880
I can not only remove the brand on your head,

93
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,940
but also free you from your slave status.

94
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:53,540
The conditions you mentioned are indeed tempting.

95
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:56,360
But I really don't know what you are talking about.

96
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:58,760
It doesn't matter.

97
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:01,560
As long as you become our spy,

98
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:04,160
join Fang Ji's imperial envoy team,

99
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:07,400
and put the things I give you into the Fang family,

100
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:10,880
my previous offer still stands.

101
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:15,000
You have already taken the Gu bug I refined.

102
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,930
If you dare to betray me,

103
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:19,040
I just need to blow the bamboo whistle

104
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:21,520
to awaken the Gu bug and take your life.

105
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:26,880
Do you want to avenge your sister?

106
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,760
Can I?

107
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:36,760
But those salt officials,

108
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:38,840
they have so much power.

109
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,000
This is a kind of Gu bug.

110
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:46,800
Once inhaled,

111
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,120
it will paralyze them.

112
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:53,000
Now that corrupt officials are in power,

113
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:55,760
the ghosts should come out to clean up the filth.

114
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:04,040
Do you like my outfit?

115
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:12,200
I heard Lord Xiong made Daxian's wife dress up as a ghost

116
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:15,920
to scare the salt makers into helping steal salt.

117
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:17,880
What a brilliant mind.

118
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,720
I truly admire you.

119
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:24,920
My Lord specifically sent me to reward you.

120
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:29,720
You little minx.

121
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:37,920
You killed Daxian's wife, didn't you?

122
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:50,520
Right on this bamboo mat.

123
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,640
You did well.

124
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:55,360
But you left a loose end.

125
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:59,080
Lord Xiong.

126
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:04,640
You'll have to take the blame for some of the crimes.

127
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:06,600
You.

128
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:13,600
I'm relying on you, Daoist.

129
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,080
This is my birth chart.

130
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:18,140
You will be well rewarded afterward.

131
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:18,760
Yes.

132
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:44,000
I failed you,

133
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:48,360
and those who died because of me.

134
00:08:58,640 --> 00:08:59,720
Yan'er.

135
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,680
Yan'er.

136
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:02,800
Yan'er.

137
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:11,560
Zhaoxue.

138
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,720
Yan'er.

139
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,920
Wake up, Yan'er.

140
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:29,020
It's your sister's fault.

141
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:30,720
Wake up, Yan'er.

142
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,440
Yan'er.

143
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,760
Yan'er.

144
00:09:36,920 --> 00:09:38,080
Yan'er.

145
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:36,520
I understand.

146
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:39,920
This pain

147
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,040
will never fade.

148
00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:52,970
I will always be with you to face it.

149
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:13,880
Cry if you want to.

150
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,560
Fang Ji.

151
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:35,080
Fang Ji.

152
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:38,840
I miss my mother.

153
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,600
I miss my father.

154
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:44,400
I miss my sister.

155
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,920
I miss them so much.

156
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:00,800
Fang Ji.

157
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:20,440
I want to avenge my sister.

158
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:27,890
I want to find the real culprit who murdered my whole family.

159
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,560
I want them

160
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:34,480
to pay in blood.

161
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:39,760
Okay.

162
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:43,060
I'll take you to get the evidence.

163
00:12:51,560 --> 00:12:52,360
Okay.

164
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:22,760
Zhaoxue.

165
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,920
The dead cannot be brought back to life.

166
00:13:24,920 --> 00:13:26,040
Don't be too sad.

167
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:35,280
I specifically found two jars of twenty-year-old aged wine.

168
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:38,240
I'll take you for a drink.

169
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:41,280
I don't want to go.

170
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:48,000
This is what we just searched from the Fang residence,

171
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:50,450
evidence related to the witchcraft case.

172
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:58,640
It has to do with him.

173
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:03,700
This account book is fake.

174
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:10,320
Every transaction

175
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:13,200
and every bribe in this account book is clearly traceable.

176
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:16,120
It not only has Lord Fang's private seal,

177
00:14:16,680 --> 00:14:20,520
but also the confessions of countless accomplices who have already been caught.

178
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:22,480
These pieces of evidence are closely linked

179
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:24,840
and are by no means fabricated out of thin air.

180
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:25,700
Young Marquis.

181
00:14:26,920 --> 00:14:29,800
You and Fang Ji have known each other since childhood.

182
00:14:29,800 --> 00:14:31,280
If you still have doubts,

183
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:34,800
why not wait until I find the clues my father left behind?

184
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:36,880
Then everything will naturally come to light.

185
00:14:36,880 --> 00:14:38,540
Don't you know his character?

186
00:14:38,920 --> 00:14:39,800
Even now,

187
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:40,640
do you still want to protect him?

188
00:14:40,640 --> 00:14:41,970
I'm not protecting him.

189
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:43,800
I believe him.

190
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:46,000
Believe?

191
00:14:48,680 --> 00:14:49,720
Do you know

192
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:52,960
that based solely on this evidence,

193
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:56,730
I could detain and interrogate him immediately?

194
00:14:57,400 --> 00:14:58,200
Fine.

195
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:02,120
Now Fang Ji and I can be considered accomplices.

196
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:05,320
Arrest me too.

197
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:12,000
Why?

198
00:15:13,400 --> 00:15:14,280
Young Marquis.

199
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:17,280
I'm sorry.

200
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,040
Lord Fang.

201
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:21,640
Let's go.
